# API Documentation Directory

This directory contains:
- openapi.yaml - OpenAPI specification (synced from backend repo)
- types.ts - Generated TypeScript types from OpenAPI
- .openapi-config.json - Sync configuration

## Commands

```bash
# First time setup - interactive
bun run api:sync

# Quick sync using saved config
bun run api:sync -c

# Sync and generate TypeScript types
bun run api:sync:types

# Generate types only (spec must exist)
bun run api:types
```

## MCP OpenAPI Server Configuration

Add to your Claude Code configuration:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "openapi": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "mcp-openapi-server"],
      "env": {
        "OPENAPI_SPEC_PATH": "./api/openapi.yaml",
        "API_BASE_URL": "https://your-api.com"
      }
    }
  }
}
```
